# Kafi Commodities — International Sales AI Agent

## Client & purpose

Build a **sales co-pilot** (not autopilot) for **Kafi Commodities (Pvt) Ltd** — Pakistani food exporter since 1982. Products include **rice** (Basmati/non-Basmati), **chutney, sauces, pickles**, **Himalayan pink salt** (Essence brand), spices, recipe mixes, honey, and related staples. Markets: Middle East, Europe, Africa, North America, Asia. Certifications: ISO, HACCP, Halal.

**Ideal buyers:** importers, distributors, wholesale food traders, supermarket/retail chains, HORECA suppliers — and **individual traders/importers** (sole proprietors, brokers). Leads can be **companies or individuals**; filter by type, country, product fit, and score.

**Core principle:** Every outbound message (email, WhatsApp, DM) is a **draft** until a human approves via the dashboard.

